title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Although small, the Flint plant produces several million rivets of varying size each week.” [From an article by John Griffiths in The Financial Times, 30 November 1993. Submitted by Anon., Los Angeles.]
